<h3><a id="available_online"></a> Q: Is the Transport Test Tool (T3) available for use online (in the cloud)?</h3>

<p>A: Yes, NIST maintains a web version at <a href="http://hit-testing.nist.gov:9100/ttt">http://hit-testing.nist.gov:9100/ttt</a>.  Because this is a public copy
there are a few restrictions.  For example, new SOAP endpoints cannot be added.  To have this update/configuration 
capability you need to run your own copy where you will have update rights.</p>

<hr>

